name: Passage to Heaven - Alpha
description:
This creation is a gateway to the final works based on the GALATICA 100 artworks, created during the powerful and unforgiving lockdowns, early 2021.

It is a mix of Acrylic Painting, Digital Photography, and 3D raytracing.

It is a unique piece, and part of my artistic research. Each artwork of the Passage to Heaven collection is associated to a Greek letter.
